    pointsExtractActions.setExtractStatus(PointsExtractStatus.ERROR);
  } else {
    pointsExtractActions.setLoadingMore(false);
  }

  eventServerResponse(ANALYTICS_EVENTS.EXTRACT_ERROR);
}
```

**Problem**: If error occurs while loading page 2, `handleError()` retries page 1 only. User loses pagination context. Should retry the same page that failed, not always page 1.

